---
source: tests/parser.rs
expression: "tree(\"% c\\n\\\\section{A}\")"
---
ROOT@0..15
  PARAGRAPH@0..15
    COMMAND@0..15
      COMMENT@0..3 "% c"
      NEWLINE@3..4 "\n"
      CONTROL_WORD@4..12 "\\section"
      GROUP@12..15
        L_BRACE@12..13 "{"
        WORD@13..14 "A"
        R_BRACE@14..15 "}"
